@node History

Changes
-------
    V 2.0
    -----
    o wheelmouse support
    o line length per date no longer restricted
    o position and size of window configurable
    o option SCREEN/K added
    o important dates may be rendered in boldface with "!",
      see @{"Characters with special meaning" link "Data"16}
    o ToolTypes may be used for configuration
    o weeknumbers now correctly calculated according to ISO 8601 standard
    o events occuring on 29th of february can now be entered. They will
      be displayed in leap years only
    o gadget slightly rearranged
    o a lot of small improvements

    V 2.1
    -----
    o added file requesters for opening and saving data files
    o the date command (button D or key D) now also shows the
      difference between date entered and current day

    @{" back " link "main"}

@endnode

